1. *Vašeg* domaćina poštujemo. (We respect your host.)
2. Nema problema, *vašeg* psa ćemo pažljivo čuvati. (No problem, we will carefully look after your dog.)
3. *Vašeg* oca smo upoznali pre nekoliko godina. (We met your father a few years ago.)
4. Trebalo bi da poštujete *vašeg* nastavnika. (You should respect your teacher.)
5. Svi smo srećni što je *vašeg* sina promovisao. (We are all happy that your son was promoted.)